            "title": "台股收市靠穩",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台灣股市靠穩。加權指數收市報21968點，升6點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">指數本周累計跌約2.7%。</p>\n</div>",
